2) MENU with a LOGO has to offer the following options:(1,5p)

 2.1) Home: A link that reloads the initial web.(0,25pt)

 2.2) Products: Shows in the Main Division a list of products categories (at least two), that when selected shows the corresponding items (0,25pt)

 2.3) About: Shows information in the Main Division about the Company.(0,25pt)

 2.4) Sign in: Lets us sign in to the web or in case we are no member it displays a form for registering .(0,25pt)

 2.5) Cart: Shows the content of our shopping cart in the Main division and confirms or cancel the order.

 2.6) Language: Lets you switch the languages (at least Spanish and English).(0.5pt.)

